。事实上，对于李磊的技术能力与意志品质，主教练伊万科维奇也都给予了充分肯定。此外，本期集训归队的另一位泰山后卫高准翼，曾经在俱乐部队及国家队出任过左边后卫。而在中、日比赛前的球队分组对抗训练期间，年轻球员黄政宇亦客串过左后卫。因此，教练组暂不会补充征调其他球员入队。 另据了解，主力中卫朱辰杰也因身体不适，缺席了7日晚国足的合练。不过，他的伤势可控，仍将大概率以首发身份出现在10日晚的比赛中。 按照计划，中国队将在8日晚的训练中，为中、沙比赛演练技战术。结合中、日比赛中球队暴露的问题，中国队将在10日的比赛中适当调整阵容。 来源：北青体育刘洋离队国足不再补招球员_训练_比赛_李磊"},"attached_info":"Cj8IyILfi43Q7OAJEAMaCTExMDM5ODE0NSD2s/S2BjAAOCVABnIJNjY2NTQwNzYzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"74 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5278f536d3f620fd97f1af4dfa48c3df_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1725884800.870456","card_id":"Q_661491074","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":661491074,"title":"为什么在动漫中，观众一眼就能辨别出路人和角色?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/661491074","type":"question","created":1720841135,"answer_count":23,"follower_count":26,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1522,4650,13908,15917,389551],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IyILfi43Q7OAJEAMaCTEwOTI3NTczOSCv58e0BjAAOBpAB3IJNjYxNDkxMDc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"71 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-346de9b512494105d75f079bfaa2cd76_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1725884800.870642","card_id":"Q_665311825","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665311825,"title":"猫挑食到饿死也不吃一口猫粮怎么办?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665311825","type":"question","created":1724627523,"ans